creator: Getsafe Digital GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Get the insurance coverage that sets you free. Tailor it to your needs, know that you’ve got it covered – go out and live. Life happens anyway.

More than 100,000 customers already love us. They let us know through fantastic ratings for our app, our company, and our customer support. We love you back!

SWITCH IT, CHANGE IT, MAKE IT YOURS
Insurance needs to be flexible in order to keep up with your life. Make all necessary changes easily in our app.

AVAILABLE 24/7
Our chatbot Carla is there for you around the clock. It helps you to file claims quickly and easily in the app.

BETTER TOGETHER
Share your coverage with your loved ones. Give them access to the Getsafe app. (Germany only)

FAIR PRICES
By operating without insurance brokers, we offer our products at fair prices.

ALL IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS, FULLY DIGITAL
You can find your policies and certificates easily in your app.

INVITE FRIENDS, RECEIVE CREDIT
If you invite your friends and they buy insurance, you will both receive €15 credit (Germany) or £15 (UK).

Which insurance products are available?

Germany:

Liability insurance:
Mishaps can happen at any time. Why don't you let us worry about that? With the Getsafe Liability insurance, you can just go out and live.

Accident insurance:
What if...? This question should never hold you back. Your Getsafe Accident insurance will cushion the financial consequences if an accident causes permanent damage to your health.

Contents insurance:
Sometimes, stuff happens to your belongings. We'll deal with it so you can move on, no tears needed.

Bike insurance:
Because life is too beautiful to be passed by. If someone steals your bike, we'll get you up on a new bike in no time.

Dog Liability insurance:
If you own a dog, you already know the kind of mischief your pet can cause. Let us take care of the consequences. With Getsafe Dog Liability insurance, you and your furry friend can go out and enjoy life.

Drone Liability insurance:
Your insurance for the oops-moment on your drone adventure. If only everything in life were that easy!

Legal insurance:
Don't let disputes bring you down. With the Getsafe Legal insurance, you'll stay on the bright side of life.

Dental insurance:
With our three dental modules, nothing can put you in a bad mood. Not even a dentist appointment. We offer modules for dental routine care, dental treatment, and dental replacement.

Travel Health insurance:
Don't let anything hold you back while you're on vacation. With our health insurance for trips up to 8 weeks, you can let go of all worries.

United Kingdom:

Contents insurance:
Sometimes, stuff happens to your stuff. We'll deal with it so you can move on, no tears needed.

Who is Getsafe?
Getsafe is a fully digital insurance company that allows you to cover yourself and your universe simply from your smartphone. Opt in, opt out, switch it, change it, make it yours. We make sure that you know exactly what is covered and what is not, so that when things go wrong we’re here to support you.

Security:
The security of your data is our top priority. Data is therefore always processed in accordance with the applicable data protection legislation.

Ideas & Feedback:
We can only build a great product when you give us constructive ideas and feedback. We appreciate your comments and will implement them, so send us an email at feedback@hellogetsafe.com

title: Getsafe

creator: Getsafe Digital GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Get the confidence to enjoy your life with complete peace of mind – with the right insurance for you. When life gives you lemons, Getsafe is here for you with simple, fair and personalised coverage.

TOP COVERAGE AT GREAT PRICES
We use the latest technology and do not rely on insurance brokers. This means we can offer products that really hit the mark – without breaking the bank.

FULLY FLEXIBLE
Use our app to buy, manage, adapt or even cancel your policies – it couldn’t be simpler.

TAILORED TO YOU
We want you to have the best cover, no matter what happens – so you don’t have to worry. Our insurance policies are easily customisable with extensions and add-ons to suit you.

BY YOUR SIDE 24/7
Our chatbot is always on hand to help, so you can file a claim in the app quickly and easily – no paperwork, no fuss. And if you ever need an extra helping hand, our customer support team is here for you.

IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS IN ONE PLACE
With our app, all of your insurance documents are just a tap away – ready to be downloaded whenever you need them.

STAYING SAFE TOGETHER
Share the love by adding someone to your policy. They will get their own access to the documents in the app and enjoy all the benefits of Getsafe.

INVITE FRIENDS AND GET CREDIT
Invite your friends and receive €15 in credit when they take out their first insurance policy – and they will also get €15!

Which insurance products are available?

In Germany, we cover the following areas: liability and legal, living and mobility, health, finance and occupation.

In Austria, you can take out liability and legal insurance with Getsafe.

In the United Kingdom, we offer home insurance as well as buildings and contents insurance.


Getsafe has been reported on by the likes of Bloomberg, Reuters, Business Insider and TechCrunch, as well as German-speaking newspapers Handelsblatt, FAZ and NZZ, and business magazine Wirtschaftswoche.

In 2021, Getsafe received its licence to conduct insurance business from Germany’s financial regulator, BaFin. Getsafe is now one of Europe’s ten largest insurtech companies.

SECURITY
Keeping your data safe and secure is our top priority. Your data is therefore always processed with the utmost care in accordance with the applicable data protection laws.

IDEAS AND FEEDBACK
We are always working on ways to stay on top of our game and improve our app. We would love to hear your ideas and feedback! Perhaps you’ve been dying for a new feature, have found a bug or simply have a question? Feel free to get in touch at feedback@hellogetsafe.com.

We use the latest technology and do not rely on insurance brokers. This means we can offer products that really hit the mark – without breaking the bank.

FULLY FLEXIBLE
Use our app to buy, manage, adapt or even cancel your policies – it couldn’t be simpler.

TAILORED TO YOU
We want you to have the best cover, no matter what happens – so you don’t have to worry. Our insurance policies are easily customisable with extensions and add-ons to suit you.

BY YOUR SIDE 24/7
Our chatbot is always on hand to help, so you can file a claim in the app quickly and easily – no paperwork, no fuss. And if you ever need an extra helping hand, our customer support team is here for you.

IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS IN ONE PLACE
With our app, all of your insurance documents are just a tap away – ready to be downloaded whenever you need them.

STAYING SAFE TOGETHER
Share the love by adding someone to your policy. They will get their own access to the documents in the app and enjoy all the benefits of Getsafe.

INVITE FRIENDS AND GET CREDIT
Invite your friends and receive €15 in credit when they take out their first insurance policy – and they will also get €15!

Which insurance products are available?

In Germany, we cover the following areas: liability and legal, living and mobility, health, finance and occupation.

In Austria, you can take out home and liability insurance with Getsafe.

In the United Kingdom, we offer home insurance as well as buildings and contents insurance.


Getsafe has been reported on by the likes of Bloomberg, Reuters, Business Insider and TechCrunch, as well as German-speaking newspapers Handelsblatt, FAZ and NZZ, and business magazine Wirtschaftswoche.

In 2021, Getsafe received its licence to conduct insurance business from Germany’s financial regulator, BaFin. Getsafe is now one of Europe’s ten largest insurtech companies.

SECURITY
Keeping your data safe and secure is our top priority. Your data is therefore always processed with the utmost care in accordance with the applicable data protection laws.

TOP COVERAGE AT GREAT PRICES
We use the latest technology and do not rely on insurance brokers. This means we can offer products that really hit the mark – without breaking the bank.

FULLY FLEXIBLE
Use our app to buy, manage, adapt or even cancel your policies – it couldn’t be simpler.

TAILORED TO YOU
We want you to have the best cover, no matter what happens – so you don’t have to worry. Our insurance policies are easily customisable with extensions and add-ons to suit you.

BY YOUR SIDE 24/7
Our chatbot is always on hand to help, so you can file a claim in the app quickly and easily – no paperwork, no fuss. And if you ever need an extra helping hand, our customer support team is here for you.

IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS IN ONE PLACE
With our app, all of your insurance documents are just a tap away – ready to be downloaded whenever you need them.

STAYING SAFE TOGETHER
Share the love by adding someone to your policy. They will get their own access to the documents in the app and enjoy all the benefits of Getsafe.

INVITE FRIENDS AND GET CREDIT
Invite your friends and receive €15 in credit when they take out their first insurance policy – and they will also get €15!

Which insurance products are available?

In Germany, we cover the following areas: liability and legal, living and mobility, health, finance and occupation.

In Austria, you can take out home and liability insurance with Getsafe.

In the United Kingdom, we offer home insurance as well as buildings and contents insurance.


Getsafe has been reported on by the likes of Bloomberg, Reuters, Business Insider and TechCrunch, as well as German-speaking newspapers Handelsblatt, FAZ and NZZ, and business magazine Wirtschaftswoche.

In 2021, Getsafe received its licence to conduct insurance business from Germany’s financial regulator, BaFin. Getsafe is now one of Europe’s ten largest insurtech companies.

SECURITY
Keeping your data safe and secure is our top priority. Your data is therefore always processed with the utmost care in accordance with the applicable data protection laws.

IDEAS AND FEEDBACK
We are always working on ways to stay on top of our game and improve our app. We would love to hear your ideas and feedback! Perhaps you’ve been dying for a new feature, have found a bug or simply have a question? Feel free to get in touch at feedback@hellogetsafe.com.

descriptionHtml:
Find the best insurance that fits you with Getsafe! Buy insurance, manage your policies, file claims – it’s easy, fast and 100% digital. Over 500.000 customers already have found their ideal insurance match with Getsafe – now it’s your turn!

Why Getsafe?

Insurance redefined
Get more out of your insurance by being rewarded for what you do to protect yourself. Earn Safepoints to save on your premium payments.

Top service at fair prices
We offer modern tech, personalised plans and fast support at fair prices. We make sure you’re well protected while also not spending more than you need to.

All in one app
Binders full of paperwork are not our style: Find and buy insurance, manage policies, make claims and see your important documents – all from your smartphone.

100% in English
No German? No problem! Find insurance, get help, and manage claims all in English.

Flexible and personalised insurance
Things change. Your insurance needs to grow with you. Easily update your insurance anytime or extend your coverage with insurance add-ons for even more protection.

4.8/5 average advisor rating
Don’t want to spend hours comparing insurance? Our insurance experts can help you find the best solution. They’ve got a stellar rating of 4.8/5 from our existing customers!

Fast support
Whether you’ve got a question or need help when something happens – we’re here for you. File a claim in the app – anytime, anywhere. We’ll handle the rest, so you can get on with your life. Our in-app chat is available 24/7.

Over 500,000 people trust us
We’re the insurer of choice for expats in Germany, and understand the unique challenges that come with living in Germany – and abroad too.

We’re regulated in Germany
Because our insurance is BaFin accredited and compliant, we’re held to high standards.

Tell your friends, get credit
Like Getsafe? Tell your friends and we’ll reward you with €30 in-app credit! Your friends will start with €15.

We’ve got what you need:
- Liability insurance: A must-have to protect you from costs if you cause accidental damage or injure someone.
- Private pension insurance: Close the pension gap and be financially secure in your golden years.
- Private health insurance: Set yourself up for the best medical care when you need it, personalise your policy and benefit from a wide range of services.
- Pet Health insurance: Protects pets in the event of illness, injury, surgery or veterinary treatment.
- Dog liability insurance: Be financially covered for damage caused by your dog.
- Drone liability insurance: If you want your drone to take flight in Germany, this insurance is mandatory to have.
- Legal insurance: Covers the costs in the event of legal issues.
- Income protection insurance: Protect yourself with a regular monthly income and financial security, even if health issues keep you from continuing in your current job.
- Children's savings plan: Long-term investment plans to give your kids a head start once they hit adulthood.
- Household contents insurance: Protects you against risks like fire, water or storm damage, break-ins or robbery.
- Supplementary dental insurance: Covers expensive dental treatments not covered by public health insurance.
- Term life insurance: Secure the financial stability of your loved ones in case the worst happens.

Data security
Keeping your data safe and secure is our top priority. Your data is always processed with the utmost care in compliance with the applicable data protection laws.
